<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='756000' id='t-756000'>So what's going on?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='758000' id='t-758000'>Well, it turns out that this seems to be the result</span>
